title: Ke Tumi Nandini
subTitle: Nandini, a free-spirited girl who aspires to be a medical student, develops feelings for a man named Abir. Furthermore, she strives to impress him, but he appears to reject her advances.

title: Bawali Unlimited
subTitle: Santo and Pappu are hired as tutors for Munmun, the adopted daughter of two entrepreneurs. However, chaos ensues when both of them fall in love with her and vie for her attention.

title: Shiv Shakti
subTitle: Shiva presents a graceful dance performance to alleviate Parvati's concerns, and his efforts are eventually appreciated.

title: Durgeshgorer Guptodhon
subTitle: Sona Da, along with Abir and Jhinuk, visits his student's ancestral mansion in Durgeshgor. Once there, the trio comes across a vital clue that could lead them to one of the greatest treasures.

title: Bakul Priya
subTitle: Before leaving for the city, Bakul promises Priya that they would get married once he returns. His father, however, plays tyrant and convinces Priya's father to get her married to someone else.

title: Chirodini Tumi Je Amar
subTitle: Pallavi, a rich, spoilt girl, falls in love with Krishna, a scooter mechanic, and gets married without her parents' approval. The situation takes an ugly turn when her family tries to separate them.

title: Yuddha
subTitle: Agnishwar Rai, a noble officer, is stone-hearted towards criminals and gets arrested when he puts an MLA behind bars. Filled with anger, he avenges his wife's death, after she was murdered by the same bureaucrat.

title: Khoka 420
subTitle: Krish is the son of a rich man and is in love with Megha. However, things become complicated when Megha's best friend, Bhoomi, enters their lives and falls in love with Krish.

title: MLA Phatakesto
subTitle: A notorious goon aspires to become a member of the Legislative Assembly and in an attempt to do so, he gives himself seven days.

title: PRATIKAAR
subTitle: Dadasaheb, the leader of a village, wants to covet the land of lower caste people in order to build a liquor factory. However, things get complicated when they rise up against him.

title: PRATIKAAR
subTitle: Dadasaheb, the leader of a village, wants to covet the land of lower caste people in order to build a liquor factory. However, things get complicated when they rise up against him.

title: Bhooter Bhabishyat
subTitle: A haunted house is getting converted into a shopping centre. However, a group of spirits residing in the house use various tactics to save their resting place.

title: Shiv Shakti
subTitle: Lord Shiva meets Mainadevi and seeks Parvati's hand in marriage, but he receives an angry reaction as Mainadevi insults him.

title: Aashiqui: True Love
subTitle: Three young people discover they're connected by love and a dark shared history. As their past emerges, it threatens to unravel their relationships and destroy any hope for future happiness.

title: Shibaji
subTitle: A gangster hires Shibaji to kill a judge who refuses to acquit a bribe and acquit his brother of all charges. However, Shibaji decides to quit all criminal activities when his wife attempts suicide.

title: Hirak Jayanti
subTitle: Though they initially quarrel, Jaya and Hiru eventually fall in love with each other. Problems arise after Jaya's father feels that the uneducated Hiru is not good enough for his daughter.

title: Sathi
subTitle: A singer accidentally causes a woman to lose her sight. Driven by guilt, he decides to help her achieve her dreams, while she remains unaware of his identity.

title: Bindaas
subTitle: Abhi falls in love with Kajol and convinces her family to get them married. However, things get complicated when Kajol's uncle asks him to kill their rival's son, who is none other than Abhi himself.

title: Shubhodrishti
subTitle: The approaching wedding of the older sibling brings two long-separated brothers back together. Soon the younger sibling begins to pursue his own romantic interests.

title: Mahaguru
subTitle: Rudra Sen, a brave officer and an encounter specialist, is killed in the line of duty by a gangster. However, things become complicated when his doppelganger decides to take his place and avenge him.

title: Mahaguru
subTitle: Rudra Sen, a brave officer and an encounter specialist, is killed in the line of duty by a gangster. However, things become complicated when his doppelganger decides to take his place and avenge him.

title: Antarleen
subTitle: Aniket Sanyal, a detective, is forced to resume work during his much-needed, long vacation after a mysterious death of a tourist.

title: Shiv Shakti
subTitle: Lord Shiva reveals his divine form in front of everyone in the palace. Mainadevi seeks Lord Shiva's help to solve her problem.

title: Baishe Srabon
subTitle: A serial killer terrorises the city, murdering innocent victims and leaving verses of Bengali poetry beside their bodies. The police enlist the help of a retired officer to track down the killer.

title: Amar Bodyguard
subTitle: After confessing his love, Anol comes to know that he is like a bodyguard to Ankhi. Later, she realises his feelings and sorts out their problems.

title: Idiot
subTitle: Samrat's relationship with Anjali is threatened when her cruel brother disapproves of him. In order to win him over, Samrat pretends to be a successful businessman.

title: Bhalobasa Bhalobasa
subTitle: Sidhu meets and falls in love with a woman named Priya despite being engaged to a different girl. He soon has to make a choice between following his heart and respecting his father's wishes.

title: Le Chakka
subTitle: Abir relocates with his family to Dorjipara, which is home to 11 bullets, a cricket team that is out of luck. He also discovers that the locality is being threatened by a political goon.

title: Fighter, Marbo Noy Morbo
subTitle: Surya, a college student, decides to exact revenge on a local gangster after he frames and kills his elder brother, ACP Bose.

title: Bibaho Obhijaan
subTitle: While Rajat's wife is extremely religious, Anupam's wife is a busy activist. Soon, Rajat and Anupam face hilarious situations in their marriage as they are frustrated with their wives.
